00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,500
 Objasnite mi to.

472
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:46,080
 Jako nas ukalupljuju.

473
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:50,980
 Imala sam nedavno jedan primjer jednog gospodina

474
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:55,220
